item.dc:creator: @wolfs_goal wolfs goal
item.description:
@wolfs_goal wrote:

latin, you should try to make trading.

trading wont be hard, you just have to create a few cases stating that it opens first trade screen, and allows inventory space to show. Then make the players able to put items up, probably with an itemoninterface code. Then declare the next case for trade screen two and make a button that has except for both screens 1 and 2.

this is really easy, i seen lots of 508’s like this, but it’s not special.

if i see improvement i will rep++

note: i dont rep everyone, just people who i think acually tried.
